## Beads Issue Tracking

This project uses `bd` (Beads) for ALL task tracking.

```bash
bd ready              # Find available work
bd show <id>          # View issue details
bd update <id> --status in_progress
bd close <id> --reason "Completed: ..."
bd sync               # MANDATORY before session end
```

## OpenSpec

See `openspec/` for detailed specifications.

Commands:
- `/openspec-proposal <feature>` - Create change proposal
- `/openspec-apply <change-id>` - Implement approved change
- `/openspec-archive <change-id>` - Archive completed change

